{"title":"农谣三首","authors":["刘振声"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农谣三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘振声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白马车，哗啦啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东邻的闺女回了娘家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹出来，背包袱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘出来，抱娃娃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂哥哥出来笑哈哈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“妹妹，妹妹真见外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这又不是外人家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又送馍来又送面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还拉来半车大北瓜。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嫂嫂哥哥别见笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年不同往年价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分下的园地粪土大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长了满地的好庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单等过秋回娘家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是花生又是棉花！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大生产，生产大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青人个个穿白褂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男的女的都生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没娶的闺女也下地啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村南浇上半天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白白（儿）脸蛋红答答！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小妹小妹你好劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过秋找上个好婆家！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨工队，一窝蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有老有小有青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上村西，转村南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家的活儿干个完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有说，又有笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不觉累来干的欢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问这办法谁发扬的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的领袖毛主席！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}